# AI Chat Page Implementation

## API Endpoints
- Base URL: `https://building-ai.itc-hub.ru`
- `/generate` - General AI chat with prompt
- `/object_question` - AI chat with specific object context

## Request/Response Format
```json
// POST /generate
{
  "prompt": "string"
}

// POST /object_question  
{
  "object_id": "string",
  "question": "string"
}
```

## UI Requirements
- Chat interface with message history
- Object selector dropdown (optional)
- Message input with send button
- Beautiful styling consistent with other pages
- Support for both general chat and object-specific questions
- Loading states and error handling